  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD TO YOUR WISHLIST!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/7883d1b584f9aefc58aed2d7e4fa7e81.poster.avif?t=1744052421\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/7883d1b584f9aefc58aed2d7e4fa7e81.webm?t=1744052421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/7883d1b584f9aefc58aed2d7e4fa7e81.mp4?t=1744052421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You are an employee who is <strong>tired of working</strong> in a scientific company. Planned work goes wrong and all the creatures want to kill you. Your only option is to survive as long as you can with weapons and aerial combat while challenging to <strong>gravity</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/f4f9575797a4e402de8ccf1a122ce292.avif?t=1744052421\" width=490 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/6cb28a5489c09a0540e39e164634cd41.poster.avif?t=1744052421\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/6cb28a5489c09a0540e39e164634cd41.webm?t=1744052421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/6cb28a5489c09a0540e39e164634cd41.mp4?t=1744052421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/d3556726defead7edfb806648b925f74.avif?t=1744052421\" width=490 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/ca90b7b86dfc17683ad7861ce443f84a.poster.avif?t=1744052421\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/ca90b7b86dfc17683ad7861ce443f84a.webm?t=1744052421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/ca90b7b86dfc17683ad7861ce443f84a.mp4?t=1744052421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/84027938c19829b759ac61eb481c26f1.avif?t=1744052421\" width=490 height=75 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/452228231219fb7f969f726978075e1f.poster.avif?t=1744052421\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/452228231219fb7f969f726978075e1f.webm?t=1744052421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764600/extras/452228231219fb7f969f726978075e1f.mp4?t=1744052421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced, brutal combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action packed <strong>campaign arenas</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy enemies with <strong>4 weapons.</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill long enough to earn powerful <strong>minigun</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fluid movement allows for rocket-jumps, sliding, dashing.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete on <strong>leaderboards.</strong></p></li></ul>",
